float s_desc::as_max_dst

Maximum distance between two alpha spheres The following descriptors are all normalized using observed values among all pocket found by the algorithm. These are not set in descriptor.c, but in pocket.c as we have to check all pocket first to store boundaries of the descriptor to normalize.
